# Features

standard CRUD of recipes

middleware to do more than view
    - can only update/delete the recipes you committed (middleware)
    - authentication with JSON WebToken
    - registration through some curl endpoint
        + email?

group recipes by some category for easier filtering by index

add recipes to your favorites

add recipes to a temporary session
    - download pdf for recipes in current sessions


# DB Tables

recipes
- id
- name
- ingredients
- description
- some taggable property?
- created_at
- updated_at

users
- id
- email
- password
- created_at
- updated_at

favorites
- user_id
- recipe_id
- created_at
- updated_at
